Download the project [git clone https://github.com/MenaMagdyHalem/Course-Docker.git]
Create Dockerfile
Build image from docker file [docker build -t website_basic_image .]
Run the container [docker run -itd --name website -p 8080:80 website_basic_image 
write "localhost:8080" on the browser
commit the container [docker commit website website_image]
tag the image to be able to push it to docker hub [docker tag website_image:latest ahmedsamy98/school_website:latest]
push the image to docker hub [docker push ahmedsamy98/school_website:latest]
